9.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Frupee-falls-to-fresh-record-low-of-96-20-against-us-dollar-down-5-5-since-iran-war-began%2Farticleshow%2F131166162.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20rupee%20hit%20an%20all-time%20low%20against%20the%20US%20dollar%2C%20falling%20to%2096.1650%20amid%20escalating%20Middle%20East%20conflict%20and%20rising%20oil%20prices.%20This%20depreciation%20intensifies%20concerns%20over%20India's%20macroeconomic%20outlook%2C%20with%20authorities%20implementing%20measures%20to%20curb%20the%20decline%20and%20stabilize%20the%20currency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20AI%20founder%20shares%20the%20leadership%20lesson%20Jensen%20Huang%20gave%20him%20on%20a%20midnight%20call%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abridge%20CEO%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a89b1abc4e9d88574ae67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHealthcare%20tech%20founder%20Shiv%20Rao%20shared%20the%20advice%20Jensen%20Huang%20gave%20him.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJensen%20Huang%20advised%20Abridge's%20Shiv%20Rao%20to%20love%20every%20aspect%20of%20his%20job%20as%20a%20founder.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAbridge%20is%20a%20healthcare%20tech%20startup%20that%20was%20last%20valued%20at%20%245.3%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Nvidia%20CEO%20has%20famously%20flipped%20the%20conventional%20script%20on%20finding%20a%20career%20in%20what%20you%20love.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJensen%20Huang%20can%20talk%20about%20founder%20mode%20even%20at%20midnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B20VC%26quot%3B%20podcast%20released%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Shiv%20Rao%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-messiest-relationship-in-healthcare-ai-abridge-epic-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%20AI%20startup%20Abridge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20shared%20the%20leadership%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-graduation-speech-ai-jobs-anxiety-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadvice%20the%20Nvidia%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20gave%20him%20during%20a%20late%20catch-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20once%20called%20me%20at%20midnight%2C%20and%20it%20was%20like%20on%20his%20way%20home%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20him.%20I%20picked%20it%20up%2C%20and%20it%20was%20awesome%2C%26quot%3B%20Rao%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-employee-jensen-huang-leadership-lessons-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunpack%20a%20challenge%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20was%20experiencing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERao%20said%20that%20he%20had%20emailed%20Huang%20earlier%20that%20day%20for%20guidance%20%E2%80%94%20Nvidia%20is%20one%20of%20Abridge's%20investors.%20When%20Huang%20called%20him%20back%2C%20the%20startup%20founder%20said%20he%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20quick%20turnaround.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20lessons%20for%20me%20that%20day%20was%20your%20job%20is%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20whatever%20the%20job%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20about%20Huang's%20advice.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20something%20you%20can%20do%2C%20and%20you%20can%20convince%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbridge%2C%20which%20makes%20tools%20for%20transcribing%20and%20summarizing%20patient%20visits%2C%20was%20cofounded%20in%202018%20by%20Rao%2C%20a%20cardiologist.%20In%20June%2C%20Abridge%20raised%20a%20%24300%20million%20Series%20E%20round%20led%20by%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20Khosla%20Ventures%2C%20valuing%20the%20company%20at%20%245.3%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20podcast%2C%20Rao%20said%20one%20of%20the%20things%20he%20learned%20to%20%26quot%3Bbend%26quot%3B%20his%20DNA%20to%20love%20was%20%26quot%3Bliving%20on%20an%20airplane.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20caught%20me%20like%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20I'd%20be%20like%2C%20'Never.%20We're%20not%20going%20to%20do%20that.%20We're%20going%20to%20find%20other%20ways%20to%20grow%20and%20scale%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20this%20is%20what%20the%20job%20requires%2C%20and%20I%20enjoy%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%2C%20who%20cofounded%20Nvidia%20in%201993%2C%20has%20famously%20flipped%20the%20conventional%20script%20on%20finding%20a%20career%20in%20what%20you%20enjoy%20doing.%20He%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20that%20it%20is%20easier%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20what%20you%20do%20than%20to%20find%20what%20you%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20loved%20it%20when%20I%20was%20a%20dishwasher.%20I%20loved%20it%20when%20I%20was%20a%20busboy.%20I%20loved%20it%20when%20I%20was%20delivering%20papers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%202023%20podcast.%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20loved%20every%20single%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-nvidia-ceo-jensen-huang-prefers-group-problem-solving-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eday%20at%20Nvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I've%20ever%20had%2C%20and%20I%20just%20learned%20to%20love%20what%20I'm%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabridge-founder-shiv-rao-advice-jensen-huang-nvidia-career-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779077296000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0a8a16abc4e9d88574ae68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabridge-founder-shiv-rao-advice-jensen-huang-nvidia-career-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jensen%20Huang%20advised%20Abridge%20cofounder%20Shiv%20Rao%20to%20love%20ever