2The%20crew%20members%20are%20in%20a%20stable%20condition%20after%20the%20jets%20crashed%20mid-air%20during%20a%20demonstration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc62x01n0dl5o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20started%20a%20publishing%20gig%20outside%20my%20day%20job%20to%20see%20if%20a%20creative%20side%20hustle%20could%20break%20even%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tse%20Hao%20Guang's%20headshot.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ef0c2ba98bc8fdc096f209%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETse%20Hao%20Guang%20started%20a%20literary%20publishing%20business%20while%20working%20as%20a%20researcher.%3Cp%3ETse%20Hao%20Guang%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETse%20Hao%20Guang%20is%20a%20researcher%20and%20writer%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20started%20a%20side%20project%20publishing%20literary%20pamphlets%20that%20spotlight%20emerging%20writers'%20works.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20wanted%20to%20show%20that%20a%20creative%20venture%20does%20not%20have%20to%20bleed%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Tse%20Hao%20Guang%2C%20a%2038-year-old%20researcher%20and%20writer%20based%20in%20Singapore.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20a%20creative%20publishing%20project%20to%20spotlight%20emerging%20writers%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20not%20losing%20money%20doing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20journey%20in%20literature%20began%20when%20I%20was%20young%2C%20traveling%20to%20meet%20my%20dad's%20side%20of%20the%20family%20in%20suburban%20Canada%20during%20the%20holidays.%20There%20was%20nothing%20to%20do%2C%20and%20I'd%20beg%20my%20uncle%20to%20drive%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20library%2C%2020%20minutes%20away%2C%20and%20borrow%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftricks-get-kids-interested-reading-books-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehuge%20stacks%20of%20books%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202015%2C%20I've%20published%20two%20books%20of%20my%20own%20and%20edited%20several%20anthologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20very%2C%20very%20rare%20that%20you%20can%20survive%20just%20by%20writing%20books.%20When%20I%20was%20a%20freelance%20writer%2C%20I%20taught%20writing%20workshops%20at%20schools%20and%20universities%20and%20did%20copywriting%20gigs.%20It%20tired%20me%20out%2C%20because%20client%20writing%20and%20creative%20writing%20used%20similar%20parts%20of%20my%20brain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20work%20full%20time%20as%20a%20strategic%20foresight%20researcher.%20Earning%20a%20stable%20salary%20has%20removed%20the%20pressure%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswore-never-kill-kids-career-dreams-became-a-mom-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emake%20money%20from%20my%20writing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20allowing%20me%20to%20pursue%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-side-hustle-creativity-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreative%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20projects%20is%20Paper%20Jam%2C%20an%20annual%20publication%20that%20spotlights%20Singaporean%20writers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d9e537c-6d2c-4db8-be37-bca5946e199c%5C%22%3EStarting%20Paper%20Jam%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20gap%20I%20saw%20for%20emerging%20writers%20was%20that%20when%20they%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-artists-snail-mail-clubs-analogue-stable-paycheck-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshowcase%20their%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20are%20only%20a%20few%20avenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20can%20either%20publish%20in%20a%20journal%20alongside%20many%20other%20writers%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20their%20solo%20work%2C%20or%20amass%20enough%20stories%20to%20create%20their%20own%20manuscript%2C%20which%20has%20a%20much%20higher%20bar%20to%20entry.%20They%20would%20also%20need%20to%20print%20up%20to%201%2C000%20copies%20for%20their%20first%20run%2C%20which%20is%20tricky%20to%20manage%20financially%20and%20inventory-wise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20noticed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-hustle-hawker-economy-gen-z-millennials-reject-corporate-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethat%20Singapore%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20have%20a%20flourishing%20independent%20zine%20culture%20like%20other%20countries%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20for%20Paper%20Jam%2C%20a%20literary%20pamphlets%20publishing%20venture.%20I%20received%20funding%20from%20Sing%20Lit%20Station%2C%20a%20Singapore-based%20nonprofit%20that%20supports%20local%20writers%2C%20and%20launched%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226b64dfa5-4d19-4da9-aff8-e8e3b435b442%5C%22%3ELimited%20copies%20for%20exclusivity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Paper%20Jam%20only%20produces%20100%20copies%20of%20each%20pamphlet.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f02332367066d7c2971b2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPaper%20Jam%20only%20produces%20100%20copies%20of%20each%20pamphlet%20to%20maintain%20exclusivity.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20was%20that%20I'd%20pick%20three%20writers%20each%20year%20via%20an%20open%20call%20on%20Instagram%2C%20and%20each%20would%20write%20a%2028-page%20pamphlet.%20For%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20I've%20put%20out%20the%20open%20call%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20editing%2C%20I%20tend%20to%20over-suggest%2C%20giving%20them%20many%20edits.%20I%20expect%20them%20to%20push%20back%20and%20encourage%20them%20to%20disagree%20with%20me%20until%20we%20find%20a%20middle%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20print%20only%20100%20copies%20each%20of%20the%20three%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA5-sized%20pamphlets%20and%20not%20reprint%20if%20they%20went%20out%20of%20stock.%20The%20idea%20is%20that%20a%20pamphlet%20isn't%20meant%20to%20stay%20forever.%20The%20appeal%20of%20it%20is%20that%20it's%20a%20limited%20edition%2C%20something%20they%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20buy%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20in%20September%2C%20I%20sell%20the%20pamphlets%20at%20bookstores%20in%20Singapore%20and%20at%20literary%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220be2b75a-4bd0-48ba-a081-0461310a2f43%5C%22%3EWon't%20lose%20you%20money%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20back%20covers%20of%20Paper%20Jam's%20pamphlets.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f0239a367066d7c2971b30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20wanted%20to%20prove%20that%20this%20venture%20would%20not%20cost%20me%20money.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20start%2C%20I%20set%20a%20constraint%20on%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20the%20business%20may%20not%20make%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20but%20it%20shouldn't%20cost%20me%20any.%20And%20so%20far%2C%20we%20have%20been%20successful%20in%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20I%20priced%20the%20300%20pamphlets%20at%20SG%2416%20each%2C%20and%20in%202025%2C%20I%20raised%20the%20price%20to%20SG%2418.%20The%20cost%20of%20producing%2C%20without%20design%20and%20labor%20costs%2C%20is%20roughly%20SG%242%2C000%20to%20SG%243%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20past%20two%20years%2C%20we've%20about%20broken%20even.%20Last%20year%2C%20we%20earned%20a%20bit%20more%2C%20and%20I've%20used%20that%20money%20to%20hire%20an%20intern%20to%20help%20me%20with%20this%20year's%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20think%20about%20this%20project%20as%20a%20way%20to%20earn%20extra%20money%2C%20it%20doesn't%20work.%20You%20can%20earn%20a%20lot%20more%20easily%20by%20doing%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20see%20it%20as%20a%20success%20that%20we%20don't%20lose%20money.%20It's%20not%20a%20vanity%20project%20where%20you%20spend%20too%20much%2C%20and%20the%20readership%20is%20too%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaper%20Jam's%20intent%20has%20always%20been%20to%20publish%20works%20that%20would%20not%20have%20seen%20the%20light%20of%20day%20otherwise.%20That's%20been%20the%20value%20of%20it%20to%20me%2C%20so%20I%20see%20it%20as%20a%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-millennial-publishing-creative-side-hustle-paper-jam-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779062881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ef0c2ba98bc8fdc096f209%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingapore-millennial-publishing-creative-side-hustle-paper-jam-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tse%20Hao%20Guang%2C%20a%20researcher%20and%20writer%20from%20Singapore%2C%20started%20a%20side%20project%20publishing%20literary%20pamphlets%20that%20spotlight%20emerging%20writers'%20works.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abharade%40insider.com%20(Aditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Karuppu'%20BO%20day%203%3A%20Crosses%20Rs%20120.75%20crore%20worldwide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779062788000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131163883%2Cimgsize-111824.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fkaruppu-box-office-collections-day-3-updated-suriya-and-trisha-krishnan-starrer-crosses-rs-120-75-crore-worldwide%2Farticleshow%2F131163877.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align