.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224779%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%20posing%20on%20the%20beach%20in%20Hua%20Hin%2C%20Thailand.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e5aee83fecbb42897a1918%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223584%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20living%20abroad%20for%20eight%20years%2C%20Kevin%20Elliott%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Camille%2C%20decided%20to%20retire%20in%20Thailand%20rather%20than%20return%20to%20the%20US.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Kevin%20Elliott.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKevin%20Elliott%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Camille%2C%20moved%20from%20the%20US%20to%20Qatar%20for%20his%20job.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEight%20years%20later%2C%20when%20it%20was%20time%20for%20him%20to%20retire%2C%20they%20chose%20not%20to%20return%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInstead%2C%20they%20moved%20to%20Hua%20Hin%2C%20a%20beach%20town%20in%20Thailand%2C%20where%20they%20live%20with%20their%20four%20dogs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Kevin%20Elliott's%20job%20in%20Qatar%20ended%2C%20he%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Camille%2C%20had%20to%20decide%20quickly%20where%20to%20retire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20spent%20nearly%20eight%20years%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-mom-quit-job-expat-move-abroad-qatar-singapore-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20Doha%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20moving%20from%20South%20Carolina%20in%202018%20for%20Kevin's%20job.%20Life%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20took%20some%20getting%20used%20to%2C%20especially%20the%20heat%20and%20the%20language%20barrier%20when%20dealing%20with%20bureaucracy.%20But%20once%20they%20settled%20in%2C%20they%20built%20a%20social%20life%20and%20traveled%20extensively%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20fun%2C%26quot%3B%20Kevin%2C%20now%2063%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmove-to-qatar-better-quality-of-life-family-thriving-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong-term%20in%20Doha%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20never%20their%20plan%2C%20nor%20did%20they%20want%20to%20return%20to%20the%20US%2C%20given%20the%20political%20divide%20and%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretiree-penang-malaysia-mm2h-retirement-abroad-affordable-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraveled%20to%20Malaysia%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Thailand%20over%20the%20years%20and%20later%20visited%20Costa%20Rica%20and%20Panama%20to%20explore%20them%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-retirement-plans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretirement%20options%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20we%20always%20tried%20to%20look%20at%20was%2C%20'Where%20could%20we%20live%20off%20of%20our%20Social%20Security%20alone%3F'%26quot%3B%20Kevin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20Thailand%20won%2C%20with%20its%20lower%20cost%20of%20living%20and%20relatively%20accessible%20retirement%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222003%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20house.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e882e4a98bc8fdc096d474%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221502%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20knew%20they%20didn't%20want%20to%20return%20to%20the%20US%2C%20given%20the%20political%20divide%20and%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20living.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Kevin%20Elliott.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Kevin's%20contract%20ended%2C%20the%20couple%20traveled%20to%20Hua%20Hin%2C%20a%20coastal%20town%20about%2090%20miles%20southwest%20of%20Bangkok%2C%20in%20November%20to%20see%20if%20it%20could%20check%20all%20the%20boxes%20in%20their%20long-term%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20about%20a%20month%20before%20their%20visas%20in%20Qatar%20expired%2C%20they%20were%20on%20a%20tight%20timeline.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20compressed%20schedule%20because%20my%20goal%20was%2C%20at%20least%2C%20by%20the%20time%20we%20flew%20back%20to%20Doha%2C%20we%20had%20to%20sign%20a%20lease%2C%26quot%3B%20Kevin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b663889-637a-4b55-94a2-6d615ab52674%5C%22%3EThailand%2C%20their%20next%20chapter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20Qatar%2C%20they%20teed%20up%20their%20Thailand%20retirement%20visas%20and%20pet%20relocation%20plans.%20Bringing%20their%20two%20dogs%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Pomeranian%20and%20a%20Mauzer%20%E2%80%94%20to%20Thailand%20cost%20about%20%24750%20between%20paperwork%20and%20airline%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20moved%20to%20Hua%20Hin%20on%20January%201%2C%20settling%20into%20their%20two-story%20home%20in%20a%20gated%20community.%20Rent%20is%2028%2C000%20Thai%20baht%2C%20or%20about%20%24870%2C%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20neighborhood.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e88314367066d7c296f71b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20live%20in%20a%20house%20in%20a%20gated%20community%20in%20Hua%20Hin.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Kevin%20Elliott.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20paying%208%2C000%20Qatari%20riyal%2C%20or%20about%20%242%2C100%2C%20for%20a%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20Doha%2C%20their%20new%20three-bedroom%20house%20with%20a%20yard%20felt%20like%20a%20major%20upgrade.%20The%20neighborhood's%20greenery%20and%20space%20also%20reminded%20Camille%20of%20Jamaica%2C%20where%20she%20grew%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20it%20needed%20work%2C%20but%20I%20loved%20what%20I%20saw%2C%26quot%3B%20Camille%2C%2062%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20neighborhood%20has%20its%20quirks%2C%20too%2C%20including%20monkeys%20that%20occasionally%20show%20up%20in%20their%20yard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20a%20bonus%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20know.%20At%20some%20point%2C%20it%20might%20not.%20But%20we%20kind%20of%20like%20watching%20the%20monkeys%20because%20we're%20not%20used%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Kevin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20while%2C%20the%20couple%20relied%20on%20a%20ride-hailing%20app%20for%20food%2C%20groceries%2C%20and%20transportation.%20After%20they%20borrowed%20a%20friend's%20car%2C%20they%20plan%20to%20buy%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222347%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20room.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e5ad2b3fecbb42897a1912%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221760%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20prices%20are%20generally%20lower%20than%20in%20the%20US%2C%20they%20said%20expenses%20can%20still%20creep%20up%20if%20they're%20not%20careful.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Kevin%20Elliott.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20goal%20is%20to%20keep%20their%20monthly%20expenses%20under%20%242%2C500%2C%20though%20they're%20still%20getting%20a%20clear%20sense%20of%20their%20spending.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20just%20starting%20to%20get%20out%20of%20that%20phase%20of%20buying%20stuff%20for%20the%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Kevin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20still%20waiting%20to%20file%20their%20Social%20Security%2C%20but%20estimate%20they'll%20get%20about%20%244%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-thailand-tourists-same-mistakes-street-food-tours-bangkok-phuket-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethings%20in%20Thailand%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20inexpensive%20by%20US%20standards%2C%20they%20say%20costs%20can%20add%20up%20quickly%20if%20they%20don't%20pay%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20always%20comparing%20to%20Doha%20or%20the%20US%2C%20you%20forget%20that%20at%20some%20point%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20Thai%20affordable.%20I'm%20in%20Thailand.%20Is%20this%20affordable%3F%20Not%20compared%20to%20the%20US%20and%20Doha%2C%20because%20you'll%20overspend%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20that%2C%20they%20said%20the%20move%20has%20given%20them%20a%20quality%20of%20life%20they%20don't%20think%20they%20could%20replicate%20in%20the%20US.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Camille%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20can%20eat%20better%20for%20less%2C%20Kevin%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20eating%20a%20lot%20of%20seafood%2C%20fresh%20vegetables%2C%20and%20fruits%20here.%20If%20we%20tried%20to%20do%20that%20in%20the%20US%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%2C%20it%20would%20probably%20be%20cost-prohibitive%2C%20especially%20in%20retirement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThailand%20also%20has%20a%20robust%20healthcare%20system.%20More%20importantly%2C%20they%20said%20they've%20never%20felt%20unsafe%20living%20there%2C%20unlike%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20gun%20violence%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dfba2b13-2d13-43b1-b34f-f82785c4db49%5C%22%3EA%20new%20country%2C%20a%20new%20rhythm%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20it's%20difficult%20to%20determine%20exactly%20how%20many%20American%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-florida-cop-moved-to-chiang-mai-thailand-cheaper-safer-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretirees%20live%20in%20Thailand%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20least%207%2C178%20retirees%20there%20received%20Social%20Security%20benefits%20as%20of%20December%202024%2C%20according%20to%20the%20most%20recent%20US%20government%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223003%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bedroom.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e883ba3fecbb42897a27fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222252%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20said%20they're%20still%20settling%20into%20their%20new%20routine%2C%20so%20they%20haven't%20ventured%20much%20into%20the%20social%20scene%20yet.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Kevin%20Elliott.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20in%20Doha%2C%20where%20social%20life%20often%20revolved%20around%20surface-level%20interactions%2C%20Kevin%20says%20that%20it's%20easier%20to%20form%20stronger%20social%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-nomad-remote-work-chiang-mai-thailand-southeast-asia-easy-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econnections%20in%20Thailand%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20the%20established%20expat%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20out%20somewhere%20to%20eat%2C%20it's%20nothing%20for%20us%20to%20say%2C%20'What%20is%20your%20WhatsApp%20number%3F%20Let's%20stay%20in%20touch%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20they%20said%20they%20haven't%20fully%20tapped%20into%20that%20social%20scene%20yet%2C%20as%20they've%20been%20focused%20on%20settling%20in%20%E2%80%94%20and%20looking%20after%20two%20more%20puppies%20they%20recently%20adopted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221263%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dogs%20in%20Thailand.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e5ad2ba98bc8fdc096c571%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22709%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlongside%20the%20two%20dogs%20they%20brought%20from%20Qatar%2C%20they%20also%20adopted%20two%20more.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Kevin%20Elliott.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20probably%20going%20to%20plug%20into%20some%20of%20the%20golfing%20groups%20because%20golf%20is%20big%20here.%20I%20hadn't%20played%20in%20years%2C%20but%20I%20enjoy%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Kevin%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELife%20in%20their%20new%20home%20has%20taken%20some%20getting%20used%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20said%20adapting%20to%20Thailand's%20heat%20and%20humidity%20has%20been%20a%20challenge%2C%20especially%20compared%20to%20the%20more%20air-conditioned%20lifestyle%20they%20had%20in%20Doha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20still%20trying%20to%20adjust%20to%20the%20language%20barrier%2C%26quot%3B%20Kevin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Google%20Translate%20has%20been%20a%20great%20starting%20point%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20long-term%20solution.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20to%20pull%20out%20your%20phone%2C%20open%20the%20app%2C%20and%20go%20back%20and%20forth%20sometimes%20wears%20on%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20said%20they%20sometimes%20miss%20the%20efficiency%20of%20getting%20things%20done%20in%20Qatar%20and%20the%20US%2C%20but%20have%20learned%20to%20adjust%20to%20a%20slower%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20the%20cultural%20differences%20have%20been%20a%20positive%2C%20especially%20the%20friendliness%20and%20openness%20of%20the%20people%20they've%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%20says%20he%20tries%20to%20live%20by%20two%20pieces%20of%20advice%20he%20once%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%2C%20it's%20their%20culture.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20forget%20your%20culture%2C%20but%20plug%20into%20theirs.%20And%20then%20two%2C%20try%20to%20make%20most%20of%20your%20life%20an%20adventure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20you%20do%20those%20two%20things%2C%20you%20should%20be%20OK.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20relocating%20to%20a%20new%20city%20or%20country%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aagoh%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eagoh%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-left-america-moved-abroad-retired-in-huahin-thailand-affordable-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779059641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e5aee83fecbb42897a1918%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F