depressed%2C%26quot%3B%20Griffin%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20could%20just%20see%20how%20this%20was%20going%20to%20have%20such%20a%20dramatic%20impact%20on%20society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGriffin%20said%20AI%20had%20become%20%26quot%3Bprofoundly%20more%20powerful%26quot%3B%20than%20it%20was%20nine%20months%20ago%2C%20and%20had%20allowed%20the%20hedge%20fund%20to%20%26quot%3Bunleash%26quot%3B%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20use%20cases%20for%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20AI%20is%20real%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20AI%20has%20impacted%20all%20kinds%20of%20jobs%2C%20it's%20been%20most%20visible%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20where%20bots%20like%20OpenAI's%20Codex%20and%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20Code%20are%20doing%20the%20work%20of%20software%20engineers%20in%20vastly%20compressed%20timelines.%20Tech%20companies%20like%20Cloudflare%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-companies-replacing-human-employees-with-ai-layoffs-workforce-reductions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehave%20laid%20off%20thousands%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20employees%2C%20citing%20AI's%20ability%20to%20do%20their%20work%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Griffin%20says%20the%20technology%20is%20at%20a%20place%20where%20it%20can%20do%20work%20once%20reserved%20for%20highly%20trained%20finance%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20blunt%2C%20work%20that%20we%20would%20usually%20do%20with%20people%20with%20master's%20and%20PhDs%20in%20finance%20over%20the%20course%20of%20weeks%20or%20months%20is%20being%20done%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbcg-consulting-ai-agents-sales-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20course%20of%20hours%20or%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Griffin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasized%20that%20this%20goes%20beyond%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bmid-tier%20white-collar%20jobs%26quot%3B%20that%20are%20now%20being%