ading%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-power-list%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20Anthropic%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20Nvidia%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20smaller%20startups%2C%20have%20%26quot%3Bskyrocketed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoney%2C%20however%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20really%20doesn't%20always%20buy%20happiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who've%20made%20it%20feel%20a%20%26quot%3Bprofound%26quot%3B%20lack%20of%20purpose%2C%20Das%20wrote%2C%20as%20some%20of%20them%20watch%20their%20wealth%20multiply%20from%20less%20than%20%24150%2C000%20to%20over%20%2450%20million%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20flips%20your%20life%20plans%20upside%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%2C%20he%20said%2C%20are%20hitting%20that%20threshold%20young%2C%20long%20before%20they%20expected%20to%20be%20financially%20set.%20He%20recalled%20asking%20one%20founder%20why%20they%20didn't%20simply%20sell%20their%20company.%20The%20founder's%20response%3A%20If%20they%20sold%2C%20they%20would%20have%20money%20%E2%80%94%20but%20lose%20the%20attention%20and%20relevance%20that%20came%20with%20always%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20under-%24500%2C000%20bourgeoisie%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20feel%20like%20they're%20on%20a%20path%20with%20no%20end%2C%20Das%20wrote.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elayoffs%20ripple%20through%20the%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20most%20recently%20at%20Cloudflare%20and%20Coinbase%2C%20which%20both%20cited%20AI%20as%20a%20reason%20for%20the%20cuts%20%E2%80%94%20once%20lucrative%20roles%20are%20fading%20away.%20%26quot%3BMany%20software%20engineers%20feel%20like%20their%20life's%20skill%20is%20no%20longer%20useful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiddle%20managers%2C%20too%2C%20are%20unhappy%2C%20Das%20wrote%2C%20as%20another%20wave%2