ul%3E%3Cli%3EAudemars%20Piguet%20and%20Swatch%20dropped%20their%20new%20collaboration%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPolice%20responded%20to%20Swatch%20stores%20worldwide%20due%20to%20large%20crowds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20fans%20camped%20outside%20the%20Times%20Square%20Swatch%20store%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20debut.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20the%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faudemars-piguet-and-swatch-divide-watch-fans-with-new-drop-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAudemars%20Piguet%20and%20Swatch%3C%2Fa%3E%20pocket%20watch%20was%20not%20exactly%20fine-tuned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrongs%20of%20enthusiasts%20and%20resellers%2C%20who%20hoped%20to%20turn%20a%20profit%2C%20swarmed%20Swatch%20locations%20around%20the%20world%20this%20weekend%20for%20a%20chance%20to%20snag%20a%20piece%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswatch-audemars-piguet-watch-fans-camp-in-times-square-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Royal%20Pop%20collection%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHype%20around%20the%20release%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mashup%20between%20Audemars%20Piguet's%20sleek%20Royal%20Oak%20and%20Swatch's%20POP%20line%20from%20the%20'80s%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20building%20since%20the%20companies%20unveiled%20it%20on%20Tuesday.%20Audemars%20Piguet%20watches%20can%20cost%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%2C%20making%20its%20partnership%20with%20Swatch%2C%20an%20affordable%20brand%2C%20all%20the%20more%20enticing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20excitement%20around%20the%20collaboration%20was%20so%20intense%20that%20dedicated%20fans%20camped%20outside%20stores%20for%20days%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20the%20furor%20had%20reached%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edangerous%20levels%2C%20forcing%20Swatch%20to%20close%20several%20stores%20across%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Canada%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20safety%20considerations.%26quot%3B%20As%20the%20day%20went%20on%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20additional%20store%20closures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20our%20stores%20had%20to%20be%20closed%20in%20accordance%20with%20our%20security%20staff%20and%20local%20authorities%20to%20ensure%20a%20safe%20environment%20for%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20shared%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20list%20included%20a%20Swatch%20store%20at%20Roosevelt%20Field%20shopping%20mall%20in%20Long%20Island%2C%20where%20one%20TikTok%20user%20at%20the%20scene%20captured%20footage%C2%A0and%C2%A0shared%20it%C2%A0on%20social%20media.%20The%20video%20showed%20a%20large%2C%20jostling%20group%20of%20people%20gathered%20inside%20the%20parking%20garage.%20The%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETikTok%20user%2C%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20police%20officers%20used%20pepper%20spray%20on%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Nassau%20County%20Police%20Department%20said%20he%20could%20not%20confirm%20if%20pepper%20spray%20was%20used.%20He%20said%20officers%20arrived%20at%20the%20Roosevelt%20Field%20mall%20at%20about%201%3A40%20a.m.%20after%20store%20employees%20called%2C%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bseveral%26quot%3B%20people%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TikTok%20user%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20ggchang.nyc%20online%2C%20said%20the%20event%20felt%20disorganized%20from%20the%20beginning.%20He%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Earrived%20at%20the%20Swatch%20store%20around%201%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20though%20some%20people%20had%20been%20waiting%20outside%20for%20hours%20before%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20confusion%20over%20which%20lines%20attendees%20should%20stand%20contributed%20to%20the%20chaos%2C%20which%20came%20to%20a%20head%20around%206%20a.m%20when%20employees%20began%20letting%20people%20purchase%20the%20pocket%20watches.%20People%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20crowd%20grew%20antsy%20and%20began%20pushing%20toward%20the%20front%2C%20he%20said%2C%20creating%20an%20uncomfortable%20squeeze%20he%20compared%20to%20a%20wave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20situation%20felt%20especially%20intense%20because%20police%20officers%20were%20shouting%20and%20making%20physical%20contact%20with%20attendees%20amid%20the%20uproar.%20He%20left%20the%20product%20drop%20around%208%20a.m.%20%E2%80%94%20without%20a%20new%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwatch%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20bedlam%2C%20asked%20fans%20%26quot%3Bnot%20to%20rush%20to%20our%20stores.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Royal%20Pop%20Collection%20will%20remain%20available%20for%20several%20months.%20In%20some%20countries%2C%20queues%20of%20more%20than%2050%20people%20cannot%20be%20accepted%2C%20and%20sales%20may%20need%20to%20be%20paused%2C%26quot%3B%20Swatch%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20those%20who%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20watch%20were%20quick%20to%20put%20it%20on%20eBay%2C%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhere%20it%20is%20already%20going%20for%20as%20much%20as%20%2415%2C000.%20Swatch%20is%20selling%20the%20pocket%20watches%20for%20about%20%24400.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswatch-audemars-piguet-pocket-watch-collab-chaos-ebay-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779034717000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a09eb00ecd7cc1332bb0883%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswatch-audemars-piguet-pocket-watch-collab-chaos-ebay-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20release%20of%20the%20Royal%20Pop%20collection%2C%20a%20collab%20between%20Swatch%20and%20Audemars%20Piguet%2C%20was%20so%20chaotic%20that%20stores%20had%20to%20call%20police%20to%20control%20crowds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A93%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%2