n-plans-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elandline%20to%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20friends%20and%20classmates%20and%20ask%20for%20playdates.%20He%20has%20been%20initiating%20these%20telephone%20calls%20since%20he%20was%206%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20doesn't%20wait%20for%20me%20to%20text%20their%20parents%20first.%20Oftentimes%2C%20I%20am%20so%20busy%20that%20I%20rarely%20find%20the%20time%20to%20even%20do%20that.%20He%20takes%20the%20class%20list%2C%20finds%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnever-get-a-new-phone-number-multi-factor-authentication-security-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ephone%20number%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20decides%20who%20he%20wants%20to%20invite%2C%20and%20makes%20the%20call%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20grabs%20the%20friends%20list%2C%20finds%20who%20he%20wants%20to%20call%2C%20calls%2C%20and%20asks%20for%20a%20playdate.%20Then%20I%20step%20in%20to%20confirm%20the%20logistics%20with%20the%20parents.%20He%20has%20no%20hesitation%20speaking%20with%20anyone%2C%20whether%20it's%20their%20mom%2C%20dad%2C%20grandparent%2C%20or%20a%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWatching%20him%20do%20this%20in%20real%20time%20has%20made%20me%20realize%20how%20rare%20everyday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flandline-independence-social-circle-kids-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esocial%20independence%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20for%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221f4e7caf-cdc6-4136-ae69-6b10063c86e9%5C%22%3EParents%20do%20so%20much%20for%20kids%20right%20now%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20much%20of%20childhood%20is%20now%20managed%20by%20adults.%20Parents%20text%20parents.%20Parents%20make%20the%20plans.%20Parents%20get%20the%20birthday%20reminders%2C%20buy%20the%20gifts%2C%20and%20manage%20every%20social%20detail%20from%20start%20to%20finish.%20We%20say%20we%20want%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorth-haven-maine-kids-independence-teacher-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eindependent%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20many%20of%20us%20are%20still%20operating%20as%20their%20assistants%2C%20schedulers%2C%20and%20intermediaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222082%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Boy%20writing%20cards%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fba16cc9dd4cb81cda7d6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221546%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20son%20started%20calling%20his%20classmates%20when%20he%20was%206.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%2C%20Ben%2C%20is%20a%20self-starter.%20He%20is%20mature%20in%20ways%20people%20sometimes%20dismiss%20because%20of%20his%20age.%20He%20chooses%20his%20own%20outfits%2C%20hangs%20up%20his%20clothes%2C%20helps%20with%20the%20laundry%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparent-save-time-procrastination-best-tips-chores-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eempties%20the%20dishwasher%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20likes%20responsibility.%20At%20home%2C%20we%20leave%20plenty%20of%20room%20for%20reading%2C%20creativity%2C%20and%20board%20games.%20We%20keep%20internet%20exposure%20very%20limited.%20We%20are%20outside%20a%20lot%20more.%20He%20spends%20time%20catching%20fireflies%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20running%20around%2C%20and%20doing%20carefree%20activities%20that%20don't%20need%20an%20overstimulating%20screen%20to%20feel%20meaningful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a91a84af-1a07-45e9-992c-4fcb9cf9d92e%5C%22%3EI%20ask%20my%20child%20hard%20questions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20very%20hands-on%20with%20him%2C%20mostly%20through%20conversation.%20I%20ask%20him%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhard-interview-questions-you-wont-want-to-answer-2016-2-25%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehard%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20push%20him%20to%20think%2C%20then%20think%20some%20more.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20him%20to%20take%20everything%20at%20face%20value.%20I%20let%20him%20lead%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20even%20in%20small%20things%20like%20choosing%20parts%20of%20dinner%20or%20helping%20shape%20social%20plans%2C%20but%20not%20in%20everything.%20I%20am%20firm%20when%20he%20misbehaves.%20If%20I%20hear%20he%20was%20not%20on%20his%20best%20behavior%20at%20someone%20else's%20house%2C%20I%20take%20action%20and%20address%20it%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20initiates%20playdates%20with%20other%20children%2C%20it%20becomes%20my%20responsibility%20to%20also%20strengthen%20the%20connection%20with%20the%20parents.%20I%20want%20them%20to%20know%20that%20the%20other%20parents%20can%20talk%20to%20me%20openly.%20For%20this%20to%20work%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20open%20communication%2C%20not%20just%20between%20the%20children%2C%20but%20between%20the%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20I%20am%20acting%20like%20my%20son's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecretaries-salaries-2011-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epersonal%20secretary%3C%2Fa%3E.%20From%20time%20to%20time%2C%20Ben's%20friends%20call%20my%20phone%2C%20and%20I%20change%20my%20tone%20almost%20instantly%2C%20from%20speaking%20like%20an%20adult%20to%20speaking%20with%20a%20child%20who%20is%20politely%20asking%20for%20Ben%2C%20or%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20playdate%2C%20or%20wanting%20to%20get%20together%20for%20tennis%20or%20practice.%20It%20is%20so%20sweet.%20These%20children%20are%20%3Cem%3Etrying%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20are%20learning%20to%20initiate%20contact%20rather%20than%20waiting%20for%20adults%20to%20do%20it%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20has%20expanded%20that%20instinct%20beyond%20playdates.%20He%20arranges%20practice%20times%20with%20his%20jiu-jitsu%20buddies.%20He%20helps%20set%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-made-new-friends-playing-tennis-we-talk-everyday-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etennis%20games%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20fellow%20young%20players.%20In%20the%20transcript%2C%20I%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20he%20has%20picked%20up%20practical%20skills%20through%20all%20of%20this%3A%20learning%20phone%20numbers%20(and%20understanding%20area%20codes)%2C%20dialing%20them%2C%20memorizing%20them%2C%20even%20understanding%20the%20basics%20of%20group%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20class%20list%20includes%20names%2C%20phone%20numbers%2C%20and%20email%20addresses%20of%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220ba3bc1-674c-43a1-b472-d3f4e26d167e%5C%22%3EIndependence%20also%20creates%20its%20own%20challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20gets%20this%20burst%20of%20energy%20early%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20with%20that%2C%20immediately%20wants%20to%20call%20his%20friends.%20I%20have%20had%20to%20teach%20him%20phone%20etiquette%20because%20not%20everyone%20expects%20a%20call%20at%207%20a.m.%20Not%20every%20missed%20call%20needs%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20four%20more%20in%20a%20two-hour%20span.%20There%20is%20social%20confidence%2C%20and%20then%20there%20is%20social%20awareness.%20He%20needs%20%3Cem%3Eboth%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20loves%20making%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-writes-8000-birthday-cards-a-year-gets-ultimate-thank-you-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehandwritten%20birthday%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20home%20from%20construction%20paper.%20It%20allows%20him%20the%20freedom%20to%20be%20creative.%20He%20wraps%20his%20friends'%20presents%20too.%20And%20when%20we%20shop%20for%20them%2C%20I%20will%20sometimes%20give%20him%20a%20debit%20card%20with%20a%20set%20budget%20and%20let%20him%20choose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Child%20writing%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fba302e1443b8dc48e2894%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22870%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20birthday%20card%20I%20really%20remember%20was%20for%20his%20best%20friend%2C%20Mark.%20His%20mother%20texted%20me%20to%20tell%20me%20Ben%20had%20tucked%20the%20card%20into%20Mark's%20desk%20that%20morning%20before%20school.%20It%20was%20not%20only%20a%20sweet%20gesture%20but%20also%20self-directed.%20He%20thought%20of%20his%20friend%20and%20seized%20the%20opportunity%20to%20surprise%20him%20without%20adult%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20think%20parents%20underestimate%20how%20much%20children's%20social%20lives%20affect%20our%20own.%20Ben%20has%20helped%20me%20grow%20my%20friendship%20circle%2C%20too.%20Through%20his%20friendships%2C%20I%20have%20deepened%20relationships%20with%20other%20parents.%20What%20starts%20as%20one%20playdate%20or%20one%20conversation%20after%20an%20activity%20can%20turn%20into%20something%20much%20more%20meaningful.%20Over%20time%2C%20these%20relationships%20can%20begin%20to%20feel%20like%20extended%20families%20%E2%80%94%20not%20formal%2C%20not%20forced%2C%20but%20real.%20There%20is%20more%20overlap%2C%20more%20trust%2C%20more%20openness%2C%20and%20more%20shared%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20practical%20level%2C%20that%20has%20helped%20me%20professionally%20too.%20Stronger%20community%20ties%20have%20a%20way%20of%20expanding%20everything.%20But%20more%20importantly%2C%20it%20has%20made%20our%20lives%20feel%20richer%20and%20less%20isolated.%20There%20is%20more%20social%20time.%20More%20time%20outside.%20More%20natural%20connection.%20More%20spontaneity.%20More%20people%20who%20know%20one%20another%2C%20look%20out%20for%20one%20another%2C%20and%20communicate%20honestly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250f67ee5-0308-46df-aa8f-cc88f0712e9d%5C%22%3EHe%20is%20still%20very%20much%20a%20child%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EToo%20often%2C%20parenting%20swings%20between%20overmanagement%20and%20total%20passivity.%20I%20am%20seeking%20something%20in%20the%20middle%3A%20I%20want%20to%20give%20both%20my%20son%20and%20my%20daughter%20the%20ability%20to%20act%20while%20allowing%20them%20the%20space%20to%20think%20and%20reflect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%2C%20these%20same%20habits%20will%20become%20adult%20skills%20such%20as%20taking%20initiative%2C%20building%20trust%2C%20reaching%20out%20first%2C%20respecting%20boundaries%2C%20and%20understanding%20that%20independence%20and%20community%20are%20not%20at%20opposite%20ends.%20They%20are%20the%20pillars%20for%20strengthening%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkid-calls-friends-playdates-independence-parenting-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779027001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fba053c9dd4cb81cda7d5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkid-calls-friends-playdates-independence-parenting-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20son%20arranges%20his%20own%20playdates%20by%20phone%2C%20and%20watching%20him%20do%20it%20has%20changed%20how%20I%20think%20about%20independence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Vanessa%20Gordon)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Train%20driver%20charged%20after%20deadly%20crash%20in%20Thailand%26amp%3B%23160%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779026880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F26%2F05%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-cctv-thailand-bangkok_7251325.jpg%3F20260517153429%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftrain-driver-charged-after-deadly-crash-in-thailand-13545087%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20train%20driver%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20%E2%80%8Cnegligence%20after%20a%20freight%20%E2%80%8Ctrain%20collided%20with%20a%20bus%20at%20a%20rail%20crossing%20in%20Bangkok%2C%20%E2%80%8Bkilling%20eight%20people%20and%20injuring%2032.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F