der.com%2Fchart-expensive-daycare-childcare-inflation-working-parents-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildcare%20and%20housing%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20higher%20cost%20of%20living%20also%20means%20that%2C%20for%20many%20older%20Americans%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-boomers-struggling-housing-costs-fixed-income-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretirement%20savings%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20falling%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F6QYDn%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Change%20since%202021%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22537%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ENatasha%20Pilkauskas%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20public%20policy%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%2C%20added%20that%20the%20growing%20share%20of%20children%20born%20to%20unmarried%20parents%2C%20who%20don't%20live%20in%20the%20same%20household%2C%20is%20also%20helping%20drive%20growth%20in%20multigenerational%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20it%20is%20driven%20by%20changes%20in%20family%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20Pilkauskas%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BYou%20do%20see%20that%20there%20are%20much%20higher%20rates%20of%20multigenerational%20households%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-im-rethinking-traditions-as-divorce-reshapes-my-family-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edivorced%20families%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20among%20married%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FOr33I%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Living%20situations%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22479%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Vanessa%20Gordon's%2013-year%20marriage%20ended%20in%202024%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20two%20had%20to%20leave%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdivorce-single-mom-living-with-parents-hamptons-multigenerational-living-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarital%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20look%20for%20a%20new%20place%20to%20live%20in%20East%20Hampton.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGordon%20found%20a%20rental%20within%20her%20budget%2C%20but%20setbacks%20like%20a%20broken%20car%20made%20daily%20tasks%20difficult.%20To%20ease%20the%20burden%2C%20her%20parents%20moved%20into%20a%20secondary%20bedroom%20in%20her%20home%20and%20now%20pitch%20in%20with%20childcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vanessa%20Gordon%20looking%20at%20her%20son%20in%20the%20mirror%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d51ee6f36fd1a78c0517c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVanessa%20Gordon%20lives%20with%20her%20parents%20part-time%20in%20East%20Hampton%2C%20New%20York%2C%20along%20with%20her%20two%20kids.%3Cp%3EJeremy%20Garretson%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMultigenerational%20living%20isn't%20necessarily%20a%20step%20backward%2C%26quot%3B%20Gordon%2C%2037%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSupport%20systems%20can%20be%20strategic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Pilkauskas%20said%20multigenerational%20living%20often%20isn't%20a%20household's%20first%20choice%2C%20and%20that%20for%20many%20families%2C%20the%20traditional%20nuclear%20family%20model%20remains%20the%20ideal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20think%20people%20would%20desire%20the%20%3Cem%3E'%3C%2Fem%3ELeave%20It%20to%20Beaver'%20lifestyle%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20this%20is%20coming%20from%20necessity%2C%20more%20than%20preference.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220fb4b99f-d300-409b-b40b-025103cc9bab%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYounger%20generations%20are%20now%20able%20to%20buy%20homes%20thanks%20to%20their%20parents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20Juli%20Ford%20bought%20a%20home%20in%20the%20Boston%20area%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultigenerational-living-build-wealth-elder-care-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebasement%20apartment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20her%20widowed%20mother%20could%20move%20in%20with%20her%20and%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFord's%20mother%20contributed%20to%20the%20down%20payment%20on%20the%20%24630%2C000%20home%20and%20has%2C%20over%20the%20years%2C%20pitched%20in%20for%20utilities%20and%20other%20household%20expenses.%20The%20arrangement%20has%20helped%20Ford%20afford%20the%20purchase%20of%20two%20other%20properties.%20But%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20benefits%20has%20been%20living%20closely%20with%20her%20mother%2C%20now%2082%2C%20as%20she%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20imagine%20how%20much%20harder%20it%20would%20be%20to%20be%20a%20daughter%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-getting-older-my-perspective-aging-changed-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaging%20mom%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20we%20weren't%20in%20the%20same%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Ford%2C%2057%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFord's%20decision%20to%20move%20in%20with%20her%20mom%20is%20a%20choice%20many%20households%20are%20making%20in%20today's%20real%20estate%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-media-container%3D%5C%22image%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22img%5C%22%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-figure-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-content-type%3D%5C%22image%2Fjpeg%5C%22%20data-srcs%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b2bb58810e27922ad4d1%26quot%3B%3A%7B%26quot%3BcontentType%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bimage%2Fjpeg%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioW%26quot%3B%3A4160%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioH%26quot%3B%3A5200%7D%7D%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b2bb58810e27922ad4d1%3Fwidth%3D1300%26format%3Djpeg%26auto%3Dwebp%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Juli%20Ford%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%5Cn%3Cfigcaption%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-caption%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-source%5C%22%3E%5CnLucy%20Lu%20for%20BI%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nar.realtor%2Fnewsroom%2Fin-the-news%2Fmultigenerational-homes-are-on-the-rise-heres-why-good-housekeeping%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20National%20Association%20of%20Realtors%3C%2Fa%3E'%202025%20Home%20Buyers%20and%20Sellers%20Generational%20Trends%20report%20shows%20that%20between%20July%202023%20and%20June%202024%2C%2017%25%20of%20all%20home%20buyers%20purchased%20a%20multigenerational%20home.%20That's%20an%20increase%20from%2014%25%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETali%20Berzak%2C%20a%20New%20York-based%20Compass%20agent%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20in%20the%20Brooklyn%20brownstone%20neighborhoods%20where%20she%20works%2C%20including%20Bed-Stuy%2C%20Bushwick%2C%20Crown%20Heights%2C%20and%20Clinton%20Hill%2C%20it%20is%20common%20to%20see%20multiple%20generations%20of%20a%20family%20living%20in%20the%20same%20home%20or%20on%20the%20same%20block.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20seeing%20more%20now%20are%20situations%20in%20which%20parents%20are%20helping%20their%20adult%20children%20buy%20a%20home.%20The%20parents%20may%20live%20in%20one%20of%20the%20units%2C%20while%20the%20adult%20children%20occupy%20one%20or%20two%20of%20the%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20recently%20worked%20on%20a%20three-family%20property%20where%20a%20father%20used%20one%20unit%20as%20his%20secondary%20apartment%20in%20the%20city%2C%20and%20his%20two%20children%20lived%20in%20the%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255f57ba6-2444-4a2d-976f-b8b04ca050b0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHomebuilders%20are%20designing%20for%20multigenerational%20living%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJen%C3%A9%20Luciani-Sena's%20mother%20paid%20%24200%2C000%20to%20build%20a%20separate%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultigenerational-living-home-addition-mom-grandma-moved-in-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattached%20apartment%3C%2Fa%3E%20onto%20her%20daughter's%20home.%20The%20900-square-foot%20apartment%20has%20its%20own%20bedroom%2C%20bathroom%2C%20and%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20kids%20love%20having%20'Nema'%20around%20all%20the%20time%3B%20Mom%20joins%20us%20for%20meals%2C%26quot%3B%20Luciani-Sena%2C%20a%20mother%20of%20four%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20having%20an%20extra%20person%20to%20help%20with%20housework%2C%20such%20as%20grocery%20shopping%20and%20the%20occasional%20laundry%2C%20and%20shuttling%20kids%20to%20and%20from%20various%20events%20and%20practices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuciani-Sena%20said%20the%20apartment%20also%20increased%20the%20property's%20value%20by%20about%20%2475%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jene%20Sena%20sitting%20in%20front%20of%20her%20bed%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d558c41a512d0a63e7346e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20loves%20having%20her%20mother%20live%20under%20the%20same%20roof.%3Cp%3EAdrianna%20Newell%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHouston-based%20Newmark%20is%20one%20homebuilder%20that%20designs%20and%20builds%20houses%20for%20multigenerational%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20offers%20one-%20and%20two-story%20floor%20plans%20for%2040%20to%20100-plus-foot%20lots%2C%20with%20homes%20ranging%20from%20about%20%24350%2C000%20to%20%243.2%20million%2C%20including%20closing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERodney%20Mican%2C%20Newmark's%20director%20of%20product%20development%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20buyers%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-gen-zers-boomers-multigenerational-housing-save-rent-costs-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultigenerational%20households%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20ask%20for%20features%20such%20as%20larger%20bedrooms%2C%20oversize%20bathrooms%20and%20showers%2C%20and%20second%20kitchens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20floor%20plan%20layout%20of%20a%20home.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69d936b505c9b303c4e77070%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20floor%20plan%20for%20Newmark's%20Umbria.%20The%20home%20is%20priced%20from%20about%20%24473%2C990%20to%20%24553%2C990%2C%20including%20closing%20costs.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Newmark%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENewmark's%20Umbria%20floor%20plan%2C%20for%20example%2C%20offers%20a%20%26quot%3Bdual%20home%26quot%3B%20option.%20Similar%20to%20Luciani-Sena's%20mothers'%20apartment%2C%20it's%20a%20separate%20living%20space%20within%20the%20home%20that%20has%20its%20own%20bedroom%2C%20bathroom%2C%20kitchen%2C%20and%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerzak%20said%20her%20multigenerational%20buyers%20are%20especially%20drawn%20to%20homes%20with%20separate%20apartments%20because%20they%20offer%20both%20togetherness%20and%20privacy.%20They%20also%20work%20well%20for%20grandparents%20helping%20with%20childcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20looking%20at%20childcare%20in%20a%20different%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20bringing%20a%20nanny%20or%20someone%20who%20isn't%20part%20of%20your%20family%20into%20your%20home%2C%20having%20a%20parent%20live%20within%20the%20home%20feels%20more%20connected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMican%20said%20homes%20like%20the%20Umbria%20resonate%20because%20they%20are%20built%20around%20that%20very%20sentiment.%20%26quot%3BHuman%20nature%20has%20not%20changed%20for%20millennia%3B%20families%20will%20always%20take%20care%20of%20their%20loved%20ones%20if%20they%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigher-cost-of-living-creating-multigenerational-homes-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779025621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a04b1de7c7e83f26041b554%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigher-cost-of-living-creating-multigenerational-homes-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Families%20have%20decided%20the%20best%20way%20to%20cope%20with%20an%20economy%20that%20makes%20it%20harder%20to%20raise%20kids%2C%20care%20for%20parents%2C%20and%20buy%20homes%20is%20to%20move%20in%20together.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22alloyd%40insider.com%20(Alcynna%20Lloyd)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20uranium%20transfer%20to%20frozen%20assets%2C%20US%20sets%205%20conditions%20in%20response%20to%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20proposal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779025140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131155490%2Cimgsize-33846.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Ffrom-uranium-transfer-to-frozen-assets-us-sets-5-conditions-in-response-to-irans-proposal%2Farticleshow%2F131155154.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%