ue%20of%20a%20college%20degree%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20for%20completely%20different%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20families%2C%20choosing%20a%20school%20can%20be%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20financial%20and%20personal%20decisions%20teenagers%20make%20right%20out%20of%20high%20school%2C%20shaping%20their%20access%20to%20alumni%20networks%2C%20research%2C%20and%20internship%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20students%2C%20moving%20away%20for%20a%20stronger%20academic%20program%20or%20better%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalary-journeys-29-year-old-finance-35k-to-155k-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong-term%20earnings%20potential%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20worth%20the%20cost.%20For%20others%2C%20the%20sticker%20shock%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-expensive-colleges-tuition-in-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etuition%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20out-of-state%20schools%20makes%20in-state%20options%20much%20more%20appealing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20good%20news%20is%20that%20quality%20education%20is%20available%20across%20the%20US%2C%20whether%20it's%20in%20the%20big%20cities%20or%20charming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-college-towns-us-ranked%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecollege%20towns%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usnews.com%2Fbest-colleges%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20News%20%26amp%3B%20World%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%20ranks%20schools%20across%20the%20US%2C%20from%20large%20public%20institutions%20to%20private%20research%20universities%2C%20and%20compares%20their%20offerings%20to%20students%20across%20categories%2C%20like%20different%20academic%20disciplines%20and%20overall%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20providing%20a%20definitive%20college%20list%2C%20it%20ranks%20institutions%20by%20type.%20For%20this%20story%2C%20Business%20Insider%20consulted%20the%20publication's%202026%20Best%20National%20Universities%20ranking%2C%20which%20evaluated%20434%20schools%20using%20up%20to%2017%20measures%20of%20academic%20quality%2C%20drawing%20on%20data%20reported%20by%20schools%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usnews.com%2Feducation%2Fbest-colleges%2Farticles%2Fhow-us-news-calculated-the-rankings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethird-party%20sources%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20ranking%20looked%20at%20data%20like%20graduation%20and%20retention%20rates%2C%20graduates'%20debt%20loads%20and%20earnings%2C%20faculty%20and%20financial%20resources%2C%20and%20admissions%20selectivity%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%2C%20while%20broad%2C%20doesn't%20include%20liberal%20arts%20colleges%20focused%20on%20undergraduate%20education%2C%20like%20Amherst%20College%20or%20Pomona%20College%2C%20or%20regional%20universities%20with%20limited%20doctoral%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECollege%20rankings%20have%20faced%20criticism%20over%20the%20years.%20Critics%20of%20US%20News%20%26amp%3B%20World%20Report's%20lists%20have%20said%20they%20can%20put%20pressure%20on%20schools%20to%20perform%20well%20in%20certain%20categories%20to%20boost%20their%20perceived%20prestige%2C%20and%20its%20ranking%20methodology%20has%20been%20questioned%20by%20skeptics%20who%20emphasize%20the%20importance%20of%20non-quantifiable%20factors%20%E2%80%94%20which%20may%20not%20be%20well%20represented%20in%20the%20publication's%20method%20%E2%80%94%20in%20determining%20how%20good%20a%20school%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20News%20has%20defended%20its%20rankings%20as%20a%20useful%20resource%20for%20students%20and%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20rankings%20don't%20capture%20every%20nuance%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20News%20%26amp%3B%20World%20Report%20executive%20chairman%20and%20CEO%20Eric%20Gertler%20wrote%20in%20a%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fwhy-elite-schools-cant-stand-us-news-law-medical-affirmative-action-ranking-diversity-transparency-supreme-court-29170776%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20op-ed%20after%20a%20coalition%20of%20law%20and%20medical%20schools%20decided%20to%20boycott%20the%20list%20by%20not%20submitting%20their%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAcademic%20institutions%20aren't%20monolithic%20or%20static%3B%20comparing%20them%20across%20a%20common%20data%20set%20can%20be%20challenging%2C%26quot%3B%20Gertler%20continued.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20reject%20our%20critics'%20paternalistic%20view%20that%20students%20are%20somehow%20incapable%20of%20discerning%20for%20themselves%20from%20this%20information%20which%20school%20is%20the%20best%20fit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rankings%20have%20also%20been%20at%20the%20center%20of%20legal%20controversies.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insidehighered.com%2Fnews%2Fgovernance%2Fexecutive-leadership%2F2025%2F08%2F28%2Fembracing-transparency-after-rankings-scandal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20former%20dean%20of%20Temple%20University's%20business%20school%20was%20convicted%20of%20fraud%20after%20prosecutors%20said%20false%20and%20manipulated%20data%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20publication%20to%20boost%20the%20school's%20online%20MBA%20ranking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20its%20rankings%20remain%20one%20barometer%20for%20school%20standards%20and%20can%20indicate%20particular%20strengths%20at%20institutions%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20identified%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-college-town-every-us-state%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehighest-ranking%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20each%20state%20on%20the%202026%20list.%20See%20which%20university%20topped%20the%20list%20in%20your%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EALABAMA%3A%20Auburn%20University%20in%20Auburn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Auburn%2C%20AL%20-%20November%2022%2C%202024%3A%20Jordan-Hare%20Stadium%20i