nix%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20every%20drive%20was%20scenic.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225034%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20mountains%20out%20a%20car%20window%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a074f95ecd7cc1332bb027b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223775%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20snapshot%20from%20a%20car%20in%20Phoenix.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20mountains%20in%20the%20distance%2C%20there%20was%20always%20a%20nice%20view%20when%20driving%20in%20Phoenix.%20There%20are%20no%20mountains%20in%20my%20city%2C%20so%20I%20marveled%20at%20these%20landscapes%20every%20day%20while%20I%20was%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20tallest%20nearby%20mountains%20include%20Camelback%20Mountain%2C%20Piestewa%20Peak%2C%20Two%20Bit%20Peak%2C%20and%20Mummy%20Mountain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20from%20the%20most%20urban%20parts%20of%20Phoenix%2C%20you%20can%20see%20mountains%20in%20the%20distance.%20Viewing%20them%20amid%20downtown%20buildings%20and%20traffic%20gave%20the%20city%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20place%20that%20I%20don't%20experience%20in%20the%20northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20in%20awe%20of%20otherworldly%20landscapes%20that%20were%20just%20a%20day%20trip%20away.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20in%20scenic%20Sedona%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6206e2493b86990018b30b35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20a%20day%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsedona-arizona-first-visit-things-to-do-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrip%20to%20Sedona%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20visiting%20Phoenix%2C%20and%20the%20peaceful%20hiking%20trails%20and%20epic%20views%20of%20the%20%3Ca