er.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20be%20active%20enough%20in%20all%20capacities%2C%20spiritually%2C%20mentally%2C%20and%20physically%2C%20where%20I%20can%20enjoy%20the%20whole%20ride%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECena%20spoke%20with%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20tied%20to%20his%20partnership%20with%20Tarsus%20Pharmaceuticals%2C%20the%20makers%20of%20a%20medication%20called%20XDEMVY%2C%20which%20he%20used%20after%20a%20recent%20health%20scare.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20pro%20wrestler%20said%20he%20was%20struggling%20with%20itchy%2C%20red%20eyes%20and%20vision%20problems%20before%20being%20diagnosed%20with%20Demodex%20blepharitis%2C%20a%20condition%20related%20to%20eye%20mites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20treatment%20is%20part%20of%20his%20overall%20approach%20to%20better%20caring%20for%20his%20body%20and%20mind%20for%20the%20long%20haul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECena%20shared%20his%20top%20strategies%20for%20long-term%20health%20and%20the%20biggest%20longevity%20lessons%20he%20learned%20from%20his%20WWE%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20into%20doing%20things%20correct%2C%20protecting%20my%20health%20and%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20bury%20a%20squat%20when%20I'm%2085.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2272bad55d-80a4-4081-8703-4fb3eb4a0e86%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20heavy%20lifting%20to%20longevity%20training%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECena%20said%20that%20as%20a%20pro%20wrestler%2C%20his%20persona%20was%20built%20around%20being%20as%20strong%20as%20possible.%20He%20trained%20accordingly%2C%20often%20lifting%20big%20weights%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20straining%20his%20back%20or%20knees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BResistance%20training%20is%20heavy%2C%20hard%2C%20dull%2C%20repetitive.%20It's%20trench%20warfare%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20kind%20of%20challenge%20has%20always%20been%20Cena's%20comfort%20zone%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20real%20struggle%20for%20him%20was%20the%20transition%20from%20chasing%20PRs%20in%20the%20weight%20room%20to%20future-proofing%20his%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20cardiovascular%20health%2C%20a%20whole%20lot%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimprove-mobility-build-muscle-longevity-exercise-personal-trainer-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emore%20mobility%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20knowing%20when%20to%20pump%20the%20brakes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223699%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20Cena%20with%20a%20Five%20Knuckle%20Shuffle%20to%20Dominik%20Mysterio%20during%20Survivor%20Series%20at%20Petco%20Park%20on%20November%2029%2C%202025%20in%20San%20Diego%2C%20California.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a074d48ecd7cc1332bb025c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222473%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECena%2C%20shown%20here%20in%20a%202025%20match%2C%20retired%20from%20the%20ring%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%20after%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20in%20pro%20wrestling.%3Cp%3EGeorgiana%20Dallas%2FWWE%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Cena%20said%20he%20used%20to%20hate%20stretching%2C%20but%20learned%20to%20love%20how%20it%20made%20him%20feel%20afterward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMobility%20and%20warming%20up%2C%20cooling%20down%2C%20all%20those%20things%20may%20seem%20tedious%20and%20docile%20until%20you%20find%20your%20why%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAfter%2045%20minutes%20of%20static%20stretching%2C%20I%20feel%20excellent.%20I%20stand%20tall%2C%20I%20walk%20smooth.%20For%20a%20second%2C%20I%20feel%2020.%20All%20the%20BS%20to%20get%20there%20is%20for%20that%20one%20second.%20So%20that's%20the%20win.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECena%20still%20lifts%20weights%20and%20hopes%20to%20keep%20doing%20so%20for%20decades.%20He%20said%20he%20particularly%20loves%20squat%20exercises%20%E2%80%94%20front%20squats%2C%20back%20squats%2C%20and%20overhead%20squats%20%E2%80%94%20because%20they%20build%20strength%20and%20muscle%20while%20improving%20balance%20and%20stability%20as%20he%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20done%20correctly%2C%20it's%20a%20great%20full%20range%20of%20motion%20movement%20that%20moves%20a%20lot%20of%20joints%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20muscle%20and%20activates%20most%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Cena%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it's%20a%20mobility%20as%20well%20as%20strength%20and%20performance%20benchmark.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dbb7efe2-4141-4087-b2ae-a2e614855c4b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearning%20to%20take%20a%20rest%20day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20career%20spanning%20decades%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-stars-who-successfully-made-jump-acting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efrom%20the%20WWE%20to%20acting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20entrepreneurship%2C%20and%20philanthropy%2C%20Cena%20said%20he's%20learned%20the%20importance%20of%20adapting%20through%20tough%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20consistent%20schedule%20of%20physical%20performance%20after%20physical%20performance%20after%20physical%20performance%20in%20a%20different%20location%20every%20night%2C%20you%20can't%20really%20get%20any%20stasis.%20It%20allows%20for%20a%20great%20amount%20of%20independence%20and%20malleability.%20You%20can%20kind%20of%20put%20me%20anywhere%2C%20and%20I'll%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20get%20myself%20comfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tradeoff%20is%20that%20after%20a%2030-hour%20stint%20of%20travel%2C%20media%20interviews%2C%20and%20other%20work%2C%20he%20has%20to%20carve%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Factive-recovery-strategies-reduce-muscle-soreness-boost-muscle-gains-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etime%20for%20recovery%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECena%20said%20he%20typically%20loves%20going%20to%20the%20gym%20to%20unwind%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foptimize-workout-personal-trainer-red-green-flags-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ered%20flag%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20he%20shows%20up%20to%20work%20out%20and%20isn't%20feeling%20it%2C%20as%20he%20did%20recently%20after%20a%20particularly%20hectic%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20essentially%20your%20body's%20dashboard%20with%20every%20warning%20light%20on.%20Do%20not%20drive%20the%20car%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20turned%20right%20around%20and%20went%20to%20sleep.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223cee7780-9293-4b3d-8906-ac39c0b40ffa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20one%20regret%20from%20his%20WWE%20career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECena%20said%20he%20wouldn't%20change%20a%20thing%20about%20the%20past%20few%20decades%2C%20since%20even%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20in%20his%20life%20became%20learning%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20thing%20he'd%20do%20differently%2C%20however%2C%20is%20ask%20for%20help%20sooner%2C%20particularly%20regarding%20health%20conditions%20like%20hair%20loss%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F21-year-old-skin-cancer-melanoma-doctors-missed-symptoms-mole-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eskin%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20only%20in%20recent%20years%20I've%20been%20brave%20enough%20to%20ask%20for%20help%2C%20especially%20in%20concern%20to%20my%20health%2C%20and%20it's%20worked%20wonders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECena%20has%20been%20open%20about%20being%20diagnosed%20with%20skin%20cancer%20twice%20after%20years%20of%20not%20wearing%20sunscreen%20while%20living%20and%20training%20in%20sunny%20Florida.%20He's%20also%20been%20candid%20about%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjohn-cena-hair-transplant-male-balding-cosmetic-procedure-wwe-hollywood-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%