e-by-side%20of%20a%20side%20view%20of%20a%20bedroom%20in%20a%20garage%20and%20the%20front%20view%20of%20the%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe4654e1443b8dc48e3705%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESofia%20Palacios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20garage%20was%20a%20blank%20canvas%20when%20Palacios%20moved%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-lives-in-380-sq-ft-converted-shed-tiny-home-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20small%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20giving%20her%20the%20freedom%20to%20arrange%20it%20however%20it%20worked%20best%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20to%20put%20her%20bed%20next%20to%20the%20doorway%20(convenient%20for%20late-night%20bathroom%20runs)%2C%20and%20it's%20against%20the%20garage%20door%20that%20leads%20to%20the%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20nightstand%20is%20tucked%20in%20the%20corner%2C%20and%20a%20dresser%20sits%20across%20from%20the%20bed.%20White%20cabinetry%20stores%20the%20rest%20of%20her%20clothes%20directly%20across%20from%20the%20doorway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERugs%20warm%20up%20the%20space%2C%20while%20a%20chair%20facing%20the%20bed%20helps%20the%20bedroom%20feel%20separate%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20garage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPalacios%20has%20the%20other%20half%20of%20the%20garage%20open%20as%20a%20studio%20space.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20garage%20set%20up%20as%20an%20apartment%20with%20cabinetry%20and%20furniture.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0206b1c9dd4cb81cda930a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESofia%20Palacios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20garage%20actually%20has%20two%20large%20doors%2C%20one%20of%20which%20is%20a%20glass-paned%20door%20leading%20to%20the%20patio.%20It%20fills%20the%20space%20with%20natural%20light%2C%20making%20the%20area%20around%20it%20ideal%20for%20Palacios'%20artwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20stores%20the%20majority%20of%20her%20art%20supplies%20in%20the%20built-in%20cabinetry%20lining%20the%20walls%2C%20using%20the%20corner%20opposite%20to%20paint%20or%20work%20on%20her%20pottery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20although%20there%20isn't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-jersey-home-renovation-kitchen-remodel-garage-addition-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20kitchen%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Palacios%20did%20create%20room%20for%20an%20espresso%20maker%20and%20a%20mini-fridge%2C%20which%20she%20said%20has%20been%20helpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20sisters%20and%20I%20love%20the%20gym%2C%20so%20we%20always%20fight%20over%20the%20proteins%20that%20we%20buy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Having%20her%20own%20mini-fridge%20ensured%20she%20could%20keep%20some%20of%20her%20items%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EShe%20also%20has%20a%20multipurpose%20desk.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20vanity%20and%20mirror%20in%20front%20of%20a%20window%20inside%20a%20garage.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fce4f7e1443b8dc48e2f17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESofia%20Palacios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPalacios%20set%20up%20her%20desk%20in%20the%20garage%20right%20under%20the%20only%20window%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-lives-in-tiny-house-outside-new-orleans-saves-money-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20room%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20stores%20her%20school%20materials%20in%20the%20bottom%20cabinet%2C%20and%20her%20makeup%20supplies%20are%20in%20the%20top%20drawer.%20A%20mirror%20with%20a%20cover%20rests%20atop%20it%2C%20so%20the%20desk%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20only%20a%20vanity%20when%20it's%20not%20in%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20garage%20has%20a%20fan%20but%20no%20central%20AC%20or%20heat%2C%20but%20Palacios%20has%20a%20small%20heater%20she%20uses%20for%20winter.%20She%20plans%20to%20get%20an%20AC%20unit%20for%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAlthough%20Palacios%20doesn't%20have%20a%20bathroom%20in%20the%20garage%2C%20she%20does%20have%20a%20sink.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sink%20and%20vanity%20next%20to%20cabinetry%20with%20artwork%20on%20the%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fcf14b3cfefc31768d6c8c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESofia%20Palacios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPalacios%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20having%20a%20sink%20in%20the%20garage%20apartment%20comes%20in%20handy.%20She%20uses%20it%20to%20wash%20her%20face%20and%20brush%20her%20teeth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20installed%20open%20shelving%20near%20the%20sink%20for%20her%20products%2C%20and%20she%20also%20has%20a%20drawer%20dedicated%20to%20her%20toiletries.%20Prints%20hanging%20on%20the%20wall%20bring%20some%20personality%20to%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDirect%20access%20to%20the%20patio%20is%20a%20big%20benefit%20of%20the%20garage.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20open%20garage%20with%20a%20patio%20in%20front%20of%20it.%20A%20jacuzzi%20sits%20on%20the%20patio.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fcf17ee1443b8dc48e2f80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESofia%20Palacios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20wall%20surrounds%20the%20yard%2C%20so%20Palacios%20felt%20like%20she%20had%20plenty%20of%20privacy.%20However%2C%20she%20hung%20up%20curtains%20at%20her%20grandfather's%20behest%2C%20though%20they%20had%20to%20hang%20from%20the%20outside%20so%20they%20wouldn't%20get%20in%20the%20way%20of%20the%20garage%20door's%20opening%20mechanism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalacios%20loves%20that%20the%20glass%20door%20leads%20to%20the%20backyard%2C%20as%20it%20feels%20like%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20yard%20when%20it's%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20sisters%20tan%20out%20there%20sometimes%20because%20that's%20where%20we%20get%20the%20most%20sun%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20have%20the%20door%20open%20and%20be%20working%2C%20and%20they'll%20be%20tanning%20and%20talking%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20so%20annoying%20in%20the%20winter%20because%20crickets%20would%20constantly%20slip%20through%20the%20bottom%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20actually%20didn't%20fully%20figure%20out%20a%20fix.%20I%20had%20to%20get%20used%20to%20sleeping%20with%20them%20through%20the%20night.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20garage%20works%20well%20for%20Palacios.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20wearing%20a%20tank%20top%2C%20shorts%2C%20and%20boots%20stands%20in%20a%20field%20with%20a%20blue%20sky%20behind%20her.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01f6f6c9dd4cb81cda928a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESofia%20Palacios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Palacios%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20really%20excited%20to%20have%20an%20open%20layout.%20I've%20obviously%20had%20rooms%20before%2C%20but%20to%20have%20almost%20an%20open%20loft%20studio%20type%20of%20thing%20is%20such%20a%20cool%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20couldn't%20get%20that%20kind%20of%20space%20living%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-built-tiny-home-texas-property-lessons-learned-tips-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eher%20own%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSan%20Diego%20is%20very%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20studios%20here%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20more%20pricey%2C%20and%20I%20would%20always%20want%20to%20stay%20with%20my%20family%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20could.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20having%20to%20trek%20to%20the%20bathroom%20at%20night%20and%20dust%20collecting%20in%20the%20space%2C%20Palacios%20said%20she%20has%20no%20complaints%20about%20the%20garage.%20Plus%2C%20her%20grandparents%20are%20visiting%20more%20often%2C%20and%20for%20longer%20stints%2C%20so%20she%20feels%20like%20the%20decision%20has%20paid%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20the%20peace%20of%20mind%20that%20they%20can%20come%20and%20stay%20here%20and%20have%20their%20little%20space%2C%20it%20motivates%20them%20to%20actually%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20motivating%20them%20more%20and%20more%20to%20stay%20longer%20and%20longer%2C%20which%20was%20the%20goal.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-moved-into-parents-garage-to-make-room-for-grandparents-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779020641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01fde1ba7ef34b41f37023%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-moved-into-parents-garage-to-make-room-for-grandparents-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sofia%20Palacios%20lives%20rent-free%20in%20her%20parents'%20garage.%20It%20lets%20her%20grandparents%20have%20room%20in%20the%20main%20house%20when%20they%20visit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgrindell%40businessinsider.com%20(Samantha%20Grindell%20Pettyjohn)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2223-year-old%20Tushar%20Kumar%20becomes%20UK%E2%80%99s%20youngest%20Indian-origin%20mayor%20in%20Bo