ldn't%20find%20a%20job%3B%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20was%20lost%20in%20piles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20came%20up%20with%20a%20plan%20to%20show%20up%20at%20an%20office%20he%20was%20interested%20in%2C%20unannounced%2C%20with%20doughnuts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20was%20skeptical%20of%20his%20plan%20as%20a%20former%20recruiter%2C%20but%20it%20got%20him%20the%20job.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20partner%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-the-internal-memo-from-linkedins-ceo-on-layoffs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaid%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%20of%20last%20year.%20Hundreds%20of%20applications%20later%2C%20he'd%20only%20landed%20two%20interviews%20with%20no%20job%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20managed%20to%20stay%20optimistic%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-search-microsoft-coca-cola-rejection-mental-health-company-layoffs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20search%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20using%20the%20time%20to%20travel%20and%20see%20family%2C%20but%20our%20positive%20attitudes%20began%20to%20wear%20thin%20as%20January%20turned%20into%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20tech%20professional%2C%20he%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20find%20work%20in%20the%20field%20as%20AI%20surges%20and%20companies%20grapple%20with%20the%20uncertainty%20it%20brings.%20Even%20with%20my%20help%20as%20a%20previous%20recruiter%2C%20he%20was%20ghosted%20by%20most%20companies.%20I%20reviewed%20and%20tweaked%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20multiple%20times%2C%20edited%20his%20cover%20letters%2C%20gave%20him%20tips%20on%20finding%20leads%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20and%20we%20even%20practiced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-mock-interview-common-mistakes-tech-companies-career-coach-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emock%20interviews%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20I%20listened%20in%20on%20a%20remote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquestions-to-ask-in-a-job-interview-2016-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecond-round%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20additional%20pointers.%20He%20was%20doing%20great%2C%20but%20when%20he%20didn't%20land%20that%20position%20either%2C%20our%20worry%20grew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesperate%2C%20he%20stepped%20outside%20his%20comfort%20zone%20and%20began%20applying%20to%20non-tech%20companies.%20But%20with%20no%20experience%20in%20other%20fields%2C%20that%20effort%20was%20also%20fruitless.%20He%20wasn't%20even%20getting%20a%20call%20back.%20That's%20when%20he%20came%20up%20with%20a%20unique%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229136965c-3cb2-4bfd-bbec-b26ed59de1a4%5C%22%3ENothing%20was%20working%2C%20so%20he%20decided%20to%20try%20something%20old-school%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20day%2C%20after%20seeing%20an%20open%20role%20that%20was%20locally%20posted%20online%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20try%20an%20old-school%20tactic%20by%20visiting%20in%20person%20after%20submitting%20his%20online%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20told%20me%2C%20I%20worried%20about%20how%20they'd%20react%20to%20an%20unexpected%20drop-in.%20But%20he's%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-i-stopped-using-self-checkout-for-human-connection-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20being%20at%20home%20so%20much%20was%20tough%20on%20him.%20If%20nothing%20else%2C%20putting%20in%20an%20appearance%20at%20their%20headquarters%20would%20let%20him%20be%20social%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20what%20would%20have%20been%20a%20workday%2C%20instead%20of%20searching%20through%20postings%20at%20home%20for%20the%20thousandth%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20serious%20doubts%20that%20showing%20up%20unannounced%20would%20work%2C%20but%20we%20were%20approaching%20the%2010th%20month%20of%20his%20job%20search%2C%20and%20he%20looked%20excited%20about%20an%20opportunity.%20That%20had%20become%20rare.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wished%20him%20luck%20and%20held%20my%20breath%20when%20he%20left%20that%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222106a9ed-c377-4742-9f89-3ff55d17ec07%5C%22%3EHe%20showed%20up%20with%20doughnuts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20my%20husband%20is%20a%20pastry%20lover%2C%20and%20on%20the%20way%20to%20their%20office%2C%20he%20stopped%20for%20a%20box%20of%20doughnuts%20to%20bring%20as%20a%20nice%20gesture.%20The%20move%20drew%20attention%20during%20his%20visit%20and%20jump-started%20conversations%20with%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20came%20home%20hopeful%20but%20nervous%2C%20telling%20me%20about%20who%20he%20had%20met%20and%20how%20the%20sweets%20had%20gone%20over%20better%20than%20expected.%20And%20it%20was%20true%3A%20his%20visit%20pulled%20him%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-diversify-the-applicant-pool-and-better-evaluate-candidates-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapplicant%20pool%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20he%20finally%20received%20a%20call%20from%20HR%20later%20that%20day.%20The%20woman%20mentioned%20the%20doughnuts%20and%20how%20the%20staff%20had%20appreciated%20the%20treat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20interviews%20with%20them%20finally%20turned%20into%20a%20job%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20first%20told%20me%20he%20planned%20to%20show%20up%20at%20their%20office%20with%20a%20box%20of%20sweets%2C%20I%20didn't%20think%20the%20visit%20would%20do%20much.%20Truthfully%2C%20dropping%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20in%20person%20for%20that%20level%20of%20role%20seemed%20outdated%20to%20my%20recruiter's%20mind.%20I%20worried%20they%20would%20find%20his%20actions%20antiquated.%20I%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20visit%20earned%20him%20the%20chance%20to%20land%20a%20job%20he%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20considered%20for%20otherwise.%20Six%20months%20later%2C%20he's%20been%20offered%20a%20raise%20and%20recently%20had%20a%20great%20review.%20We%20sti