ate%20things%20she%20loved%20about%20her%20life%20in%20country%20Victoria%20into%20her%20life%20on%20the%20Gold%20Coast.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Melissa%20Noble%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20family%20of%20five%20moved%20from%20a%20small%20town%20to%20a%20bigger%20city%20to%20live%20with%20my%20parents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20trying%20to%20bring%20the%20slower%2C%20more%20intentional%20ways%20of%20living%20to%20our%20lives%20here.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20focusing%20on%20building%20a%20sense%20of%20community%20and%20making%20sure%20we%20still%20spend%20time%20outside.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20on%20the%20Gold%20Coast%2C%20Australia's%20sixth-largest%20city.%20In%20my%2020s%2C%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-new-york-to-canada-for-husbands-job-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elived%20in%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20then%20England.%20When%20we%20returned%20to%20Australia%2C%20we%20spent%20eight%20years%20in%20Melbourne%2C%20then%20the%20last%20four%20years%20in%20Bright%20in%20country%20Victoria%2C%20so%20that%20we%20could%20be%20close%20to%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBright%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-small-town-40s-cons-hard-make-friends-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmall%20town%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20fewer%20than%203%2C000%20people%2C%20and%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20lifestyle%20and%20people%20pretty%20quickly.%20I%20couldn't%20get%20over%20how%20genuinely%20nice%20they%20were.%20It%20felt%20like%20the%20community%20really%20had%20each%20other's%20backs%2C%20and%20I%20soon%20found%20myself%20slowing%20down%20and%20relaxing%20into%20country%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20four%20years%20in%20Bright%2C%20my%20family%20of%20five%20moved%20to%20the%20Gold%20Coast%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-moved-in-with-parents-multigenerational-living-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloser%20to%20my%20aging%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January.%20It%20was%20a%20tough%20decision%2C%20and%20the%20hardest%20part%20was%20leaving%20behind%20our%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20have%20regrets%20down%20the%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20moving%20back%20to%20the%20city%2C%20I've%20found%20myself%20trying%20to%20bring%20a%20few%20of%20those%20slower%2C%20more%20intentional%20ways%20of%20living%20into%20our%20lives%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221932%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20two%20of%20her%20kids%20on%20the%20beach.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a075bcfecd7cc1332bb0323%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221446%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20family%20of%20five%20moved%20in%20with%20her%20parents%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Melissa%20Noble%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223336b550-7cf7-49cc-8842-fca8bb12bd1a%5C%22%3EI'm%20building%20my%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBright%20might%20be%20small%2C%20but%20it%20has%20an%20enormous%20heart.%20The%20people%20there%20are%20some%20of%20the%20warmest%20and%20most%20generous%20I've%20ever%20met.%20It's%20the%20kind%20of%20place%20that%20feels%20like%20a%20warm%20bowl%20of%20soup%20on%20a%20cold%20day%2C%20a%20hug%20when%20you're%20feeling%20blue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20my%20family%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-with-in-laws-save-money-better-life-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20in%20with%20my%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I've%20tried%20to%20carry%20that%20same%20community%20spirit%20with%20me.%20I've%20been%20cooking%20meals%20for%20friends%2C%20offering%20to%20babysit%20when%20someone's%20stretched%2C%20or%20simply%20checking%20in%20with%20a%20message%20if%20I%20sense%20someone%20might%20be%20having%20a%20tough%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20day%2C%20I%20even%20texted%20a%20new%20neighbor%20to%20ask%20if%20we%20could%20borrow%20a%20couple%20of%20eggs.%20It%20felt%20like%20such%20a%20small%2C%20old-fashioned%20thing%20to%20do%2C%20but%20it%20broke%20the%20ice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20I%20invited%20her%20daughter%20over%20to%20play%20and%20sent%20her%20home%20with%20some%20of%20our%20eggs.%20Then%2C%20for%20my%20birthday%2C%20the%20neighbor%20made%20me%20candied%20almonds%20and%20left%20them%20on%20our%20doorstep.%20That%20initial%20simple%20gesture%20helped%20us%20connect%20on%20a%20deeper%20level%20and%20establish%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-to-small-italian-town-left-new-york-city-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esense%20of%20community%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220616bef4-2980-41b8-9e7e-15b8791f24f8%5C%22%3EI'm%20still%20enjoying%20simple%20fun%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20in%20regional%20Victoria%2C%20there%20was%20plenty%20to%20do%20outdoors%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20time%2C%20you%20had%20to%20make%20your%20own%20fun.%20Our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-moved-small-town-lower-cost-living-benefits-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20family%20adventures%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20often%20the%20simplest%2C%20like%20packing%20a%20picnic%20and%20heading%20to%20a%20swimming%20hole%2C%20picking%20fresh%20fruit%20at%20a%20local%20berry%20farm%2C%20or%20hiking%20through%20the%20mountains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20we're%20back%20in%20the%20city%2C%20though%20there's%20more%20to%20do%20here%2C%20I'm%20so%20grateful%20for%20the%20mindset%20I%20gained%20in%20a%20smaller%20town.%20I%20rarely%20feel%20bored%2C%20because%20even%20on%20quiet%20days%20or%20rainy%20afternoons%2C%20I%20can%20think%20of%20countless%20ways%20to%20make%20time%20together%20feel%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20on%20a%20boat%20on%20the%20water%20of%20the%20Gold%20Coast.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a075ae394eb4c909fb2cfbd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20family%20recently%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20Gold%20Coast.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Melissa%20Noble%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a60fd0ba-71d0-4f28-91b4-e81b64c08fd3%5C%22%3EI%20try%20to%20connect%20with%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20I%20loved%20most%20about%20country%20life%20was%20the%20connection%20to%20nature.%20I%20slowed%20down%20and%20began%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-kids-family-big-city-to-rural-small-town-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappreciate%20the%20simple%20things%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20shift%20in%20seasons%2C%20the%20depth%20of%20color%20in%20a%20rainbow%2C%20the%20scent%20of%20pine%20in%20the%20morning%20air%2C%20the%20energizing%20feel%20of%20icy%20mountain%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20always%20as%20easy%20to%20find%20that%20connection%20to%20nature%20in%20the%20city%2C%20but%20I%20make%20a%20point%20of%20seeking%20it%20out.%20Sometimes%20we'll%20drive%20out%20to%20the%20Gold%20Coast%20hinterland%20for%20a%20hike%2C%20or%20head%20to%20the%20beach%20for%20a%20quick%20swim%20before%20school.%20Floating%20in%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20at%20sunrise%20is%20a%20simple%20reminder%20that%20staying%20connected%20to%20nature%20doesn't%20depend%20on%20where%20you%20live%3B%20you%20just%20have%20to%20make%20space%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fliving-in-new-york-city-different-than-visiting-lessons-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easpects%20of%20city%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I'm%20really%20enjoying%2C%20like%20having%20access%20to%20amenities%20and%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20spor