ompson-succession-leadership-parenting-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThompson%20recently%20told%20Business%20Insider%20how%20he%20balanced%20the%20demands%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartup-founder-balance-work-being-dad-parenting-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20a%20business%20and%20raising%20his%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20how%20he%20felt%20about%20keeping%20the%20company%20in%20his%20family%2C%20and%20whether%20he%20hopes%20his%20grandkids%20will%20join%20Crown%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20founder%20said%20that%20in%20Crown's%20early%20days%2C%20he%20spent%20much%20of%20his%20time%20traveling%20or%20with%20his%20management%20team%20and%20customers.%20But%20he%20made%20it%20home%20most%20weekends%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-parent-founder-vc-advice-juggling-work-kids-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebonding%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20young%20daughter%20over%20boating%2C%20water%20sports%2C%20and%20other%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThompson%20felt%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Balways%20able%20to%20be%20a%20big%20part%20of%20Jenny's%20life%20as%20she%20was%20growing%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20was%20there%20to%20%26quot%3Bhelp%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-things-parents-should-teach-kids-before-college-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edevelop%20her%20values%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20never%20expected%20Crown%20to%20become%20so%20successful%2C%20so%20it%20was%20only%20about%2030%20years%20ago%20that%20he%20began%20to%20think%20seriously%20about%20whether%20his%20children%20might%20take%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20family%20business%20from%20him.%20Yet%20he%20also%20wanted%20his%20kids%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgiving-kids-different-career-advice-than-my-parents-gave-me-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%