%20to%20avoid%20default.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226db93859-a655-4ec2-8b79-c755d895e0ef%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EListen%20to%20a%20snippet%20of%20Bates'%20customer%20service%20call%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22A%20snippet%20of%20Bates'%20customer%20service%20call%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.jwplayer.com%2Fplayers%2FagTDmskb-FccwB2ub.html%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20information%20was%20I%20supposed%20to%20follow%3F%20Because%20I'm%20confused%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Bates%20said%20during%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20asked%20what%20the%20next%20steps%20were%20if%20there%20was%20no%20way%20to%20reverse%20the%20default%20proceeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20would%20have%20to%20make%20arrangements%20with%20the%20company%20that%20your%20loan%20does%20go%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Sallie%20Mae%20representative%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOkay%2C%26quot%3B%20Bates%20answered.%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20have%20any%20information%20on%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20it%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20representative%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2283a07f35-d776-4a93-8f1d-7f05bd6596cf%5C%22%3EA%20day%20in%20court%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20loan%20defaults%2C%20it's%20standard%20practice%20for%20the%20lender%20to%20clear%20the%20defaulted%20balance%20off%20their%20books%20and%20transfer%20it%20to%20collections%2C%20either%20in-house%20or%20through%20a%20third%20party.%20The%20borrower%20still%20owes%20the%20full%20balance%2C%20but%20communications%20can%20vary%20depending%20on%20the%20account's%20manager%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20borrower%20doesn't%20always%20know%20who%20holds%20their%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivate%20lenders%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-student-loan-borrowers-confusion-fewer-protections-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eare%20subject%20to%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%20governing%20when%20and%20how%20they%20must%20communicate%20with%20borrowers.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20a%20default%20can%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20borrowers%20or%20regulators%20to%20track%20the%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20case%20for%20Bates%20%E2%80%94%20after%20defaulting%2C%20she%20lost%20access%20to%20her%20account%20and%20couldn't%20find%20her%20payment%20information.%20Bates%20could%20not%20afford%20a%20lawyer%20to%20help%20navigate%20her%20lawsuit%2C%20so%20she%20used%20ChatGPT%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226574%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hannah%20Bates%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa2a46405e0cf89dc873f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224383%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFailing%20to%20make%20student-loan%20payments%20could%20lead%20to%20wage%20garnishment%20and%20a%20hit%20to%20the%20borrower's%20credit%20score.%3Cp%3ENic%20Antaya%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20research%20prepared%20her%20for%20the%20first%20hearing%20in%20her%20case%20on%20March%206%2C%202026%2C%20held%20over%20Zoom%20in%20Michigan's%20Third%20Circuit%20Court.%20Bates%20asked%20the%20judge%20to%20set%20aside%20her%20default%20judgment.%20The%20judge%20denied%20the%20request%20and%20encouraged%20her%20instead%20to%20reach%20a%20settlement%20or%20agree%20to%20a%20payment%20plan%20with%20Sallie%20Mae's%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20seeing%20this%20happen%20more%20and%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%2C%20Annette%20Berry%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20after%20people%20for%20unpaid%20student-loan%20debt.%20And%20so%20if%20you%20think%20you're%20the%20only%20one%2C%20you're%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBates%20is%20now%20waiting%20for%20a%20response%20from%20Sallie%20Mae%20on%20the%20next%