ng%20cashews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20an%20encouraging%20response%20from%20the%20institutes%2C%20his%20focus%20shifted%20towards%20refining%20the%20sprouting%20technology%20for%20cashews.%20Recognising%20the%20perishable%20nature%20of%20cashews%20and%20the%20challenges%20in%20maintaining%20a%20cold%20supply%20chain%2C%20he%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20retorting%20technology%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20which%20involves%20heat-treating%20food%20in%20airtight%20containers%20to%20extend%20shelf%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20adapting%20this%20innovative%20approach%2C%20he%20devised%20a%20method%20to%20process%20and%20store%20sprouted%20cashews%20at%20room%20temperature%2C%20enhancing%20their%20shelf%20life%20and%20market%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20into%20research%20and%20development%2C%20Brijith%20started%20his%20own%20startup%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20raw%20sprouts%2C%20pickles%20to%20manchurian%2C%20soup%20premix%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20initial%20challenges%20that%20Brijith%20tackled%20was%20the%20limited%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews.%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20their%20seasonal%20nature%2C%20the%20germination%20potential%20of%20matured%20cashews%20was%20only%2090%20days.%20Therefore%2C%20year%20round%20availability%20was%20a%20big%20concern.%20Through%20persistent%20research%2C%20trials%2C%20and%20development%20efforts%2C%20I%20successfully%20extended%20the%20germination%20potential%20to%20180-200%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20Brijith%20secured%20a%20grant%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20from%20the%20central%20government%20under%20the%20Rashtriya%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana%20(RKVY)%20scheme%20that%20aims%20at%20promoting%20agri-business%20entrepreneurship.%20This%20helped%20him%20kickstart%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brijith%20foccussed%20on%20improving%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews%20in%20order%20to%20commercialise%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBrijith%20focussed%20on%20improving%20the%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews%20to%20commercialise%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20he%20offers%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20value-added%20products%20%E2%80%93%20cashew%20sprouts%20Manchurian%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20butter%20%3Cem%3Emasala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20%3Cem%3Emalai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20schezwan%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20Malabar%20%3Cem%3Emasala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20%3Cem%3Etheyal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20soup%20premix%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20brine%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20fresh%20cashew%20sprouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20meticulous%20focus%20on%20quality%20and%20value%2C%20Brijith%20priced%20his%20sprouted%20cashews%20at%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20kg.%20Through%20strategic%20partnerships%20with%20celebrity%20chefs%2C%20star%20hotels%2C%20and%20catering%20groups%2C%20Brijith%20positioned%20his%20premium%20cashew%20sprout%20products%20in%20a%20niche%20market%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20regular%20customers%20Thomas%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20corporate%20chef%20at%20Paragon%20group%20of%20restaurants%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20experienced%20these%20cashew%20sprouts%20can%20be%20included%20in%20a%20healthy%20diet%20and%20lots%20of%20various%20dishes%20can%20be%20prepared%20with%20adaptability.%20It%20is%20not%20easily%20available%20in%20stores%20so%20people%20have%20some%20curiosity%20about%20it.%20These%20dishes%20are%20repeatedly%20demanded%20from%20our%20happy%20customers%20at%20the%20restaurant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unique%20positioning%20in%20the%20market%20enabled%20Brijith%20to%20secure%20a%20steady%20clientele%20and%20achieve%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20his%20endeavours%20were%20not%20only%20driven%20by%20a%20passion%20for%20innovation%20but%20also%20by%20a%20commitment%20to%20empower%20local%20farmers.%20By%20purchasing%20wet%20cashews%20from%20at%20least%2011%20local%20farmers%2C%20Brijith%20managed%20to%20provide%20a%20sustainable%20solution%20by%20transforming%20them%20into%20high-quality%20sprouted%20cashews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20reimagining%20traditional%20practices%20and%20leveraging%20modern%20technology%2C%20I%20not%20only%20wanted%20to%20revitalise%20the%20cashew%20farming%20industry%20but%20also%20exemplify%20the%20potential%20for%20agri-business%20entrepreneurship%20to%20drive%20economic%20growth%20in%20rural%20communities.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20wet%20produce%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Brijith%20Krishnan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcashew.icar.gov.in%2Faicrpc%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FStatus-of-Cashew-Research-.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Status%20of%20Cashew%20Research%20and%20Development%20in%20India%3A%20A%20State%20Perspective%20%3C%2Fa%3Epublished%20by%20Dr%20M%20Gangadhara%20Nayak%2C%20Director%2C%20ICAR-Directorate%20of%20Cashew%20Research%2C%20Karnataka%20in%20November%202018.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757147400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1-1725551491.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496857%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala-based%20farmer%20Brijith%20Krishnan%20started%20Eatery%20Malbarikas%20which%20makes%20dishes%20using%20sprouted%20cashew%20nuts.%20Interestingly%2C%20he%20enhanced%20the%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews%20and%20helps%20fellow%20cashew%20farmers%20as%20well.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496857%2Fkerala-farmer-wet-cashews-value-added-products%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Rs%205000%20Budget%20Guide%20to%20Exploring%20Karnala%E2%80%99s%20Forests%2C%20Fort%20%26amp%3B%20Birdlife%2C%20Just%20an%20Hour%20From%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVisualise%20a%20place%20where%20forest%20trails%20wind%20beneath%20thick%20green%20canopies%2C%20where%20rare%20birds%20call%20from%20treetops%2C%20and%20where%20an%20ancient%20fort%20watches%20over%20the%20valley%20from%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%2064%20km%20from%20Mumbai%20lies%20Karnala%2C%20a%20tranquil%20haven%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F394231%2Fbest-birdwatching-destinations-india-winter-migration-rajasthan-gujarat-kerala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%